    "In our feasibility study, we had to use standardized letters to recruit participants from the waitlist of the center of expertise in chronic pain management.",
    "We acknowledge the need to adopt more flexible parameters for future large-scale studies.",
    "Furthermore, we might adjust our eligibility criterion, not limiting participation to those awaiting specialized services.",
    "This broader criterion could yield a more diverse sample, aligning with our aim to reach a wider demographic.",
    "However, we are mindful of the potential impacts on adherence and user satisfaction this broader criterion might pose."
